209
00:24:06,615 --> 00:24:07,908
<i>When I get frustrated,</i>

210
00:24:08,701 --> 00:24:11,578
<i>I go out for a walk at night thinking,</i>

211
00:24:12,204 --> 00:24:14,289
<i>"I don't care if I die tonight."</i>

212
00:24:14,998 --> 00:24:17,000
<i>I walk through a pitch-dark mountain.</i>

213
00:24:28,679 --> 00:24:30,931
<i>What's the big deal
about some guy leaving?</i>

214
00:24:32,266 --> 00:24:34,560
<i>He ran because he was
afraid of being happy.</i>

215
00:25:30,407 --> 00:25:32,618
<i>Tonight, I have nothing to fear.</i>

216
00:25:32,701 --> 00:25:35,287
<i>I'll become a warrior.</i>

217
00:25:36,038 --> 00:25:38,040
Bring it on, you damn mutt.

218
00:25:40,918 --> 00:25:42,836
You ungrateful mongrel.

219
00:25:43,670 --> 00:25:46,006
Do you know
how many sausages I've given you?

220
00:25:54,723 --> 00:25:57,476
<i>I want to bleed like a fountain.</i>

221
00:26:24,086 --> 00:26:26,213
<i>When I wander around aimlessly,</i>

222
00:26:27,005 --> 00:26:29,758
<i>I can catch the briefest glimpse.</i>

223
00:26:30,425 --> 00:26:34,888
<i>"So that's what is in my head."</i>

224
00:26:48,360 --> 00:26:49,945
<i>The feeling of being abandoned.</i>

225
00:27:17,848 --> 00:27:20,183
