going to hell together.

245
00:28:18,575 --> 00:28:21,036
I said I'm not going!
I'm not following you there.

246
00:28:21,119 --> 00:28:23,205
-Are you nuts?
-I'm free to dream, aren't I?

247
00:28:23,789 --> 00:28:25,123
I've got a great imagination.

248
00:28:25,707 --> 00:28:27,668
We'd have fun together even in hell.

249
00:28:28,669 --> 00:28:30,504
What a smooth talker.

250
00:28:31,380 --> 00:28:34,049
Why do you drag me into this?
We're not that close.

251
00:28:34,675 --> 00:28:36,176
Why do you think it's about us?

252
00:28:36,760 --> 00:28:38,220
It's about you and Hyeon-a.

253
00:28:44,059 --> 00:28:45,727
The medicine has improved,

254
00:28:46,270 --> 00:28:48,063
